  "body": "## Summary\n\nThis PR promotes **Iteration v5: Savings Goals** to the production `main` branch.\n\n### Included Features\n- **Savings Engine:** Full goal management (target vs current amounts).\n- **Interactive UI:** Range sliders for manual progress tracking with debounced API updates.\n- **Security:** Enhanced authorization checks and database schema updates (indices).\n- **Optimization:** Optimized Dashboard state handling for real-time progress visualization.\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n## Release Notes\n\n* **New Features**\n  * Added savings goals functionality to help users set and track financial targets.\n  * Users can create new savings goals with target amounts and optional deadlines.\n  * Goals display completion percentages and current vs. target amounts.\n  * Progress tracking allows users to update goal amounts in real-time.\n\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
